dc_title_s: General Map of the Northwest Territories
dc_description_s: 1 map on 3 sheets : col. ; 95 x 189 cm., each sheet 105 x 69 cm.|Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.|"Photo.-lith: and printed by the Sabiston Publishing Co., Montreal."|Includes electoral districts, township outlines, township projections, North West Mounted Police reserves and stations, Indian reserves, provincial and territorial capitals, post offices, outcrops of coal and lignite, railways, etc.|"Published by authority of the Hon. T. Mayne Daly, M.P., Minister of the Interior."|Inset: index map.
